    {
      "id": "PopularPost324732",
      "post_content": "Way back in the day when Ice Age was new this along with [False Demise](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=False Demise) and [Kjeldoran Dead](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Kjeldoran Dead) powered my UB control. Nothing finer than to steal your False Demise'd creature, smack you with it, and then sack that creature to the Kjeldoran Dead.  \n  \nThen Time Spiral went and gave us the even better though more expensive [Fool's Demise](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fool's Demise) though if you are running a control deck that cost is no worse than other control spells. Ah fun times fun times, slow though.",
      "posted_by": "edwardgr",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost324732\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_post\">Way back in the day when Ice Age was new this along with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"False Demise\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=False Demise\">False Demise</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Kjeldoran Dead\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Kjeldoran Dead\">Kjeldoran Dead</a> powered my UB control.  Nothing finer than to steal your False Demise'd creature, smack you with it, and then sack that creature to the Kjeldoran Dead.<br/><br/>Then Time Spiral went and gave us the even better though more expensive <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Fool's Demise\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Fool's Demise\">Fool's Demise</a> though if you are running a control deck that cost is no worse than other control spells.  Ah fun times fun times, slow though.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl01_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '324732'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy49343\">edwardgr</span>\r\n                                (6/29/2013 10:33:29 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                      