    {
      "id": "PopularPost184729",
      "post_content": "First, I must say how pleased I am to see the *Mirage* art, and how happy I am that *Mirage* and *Visions* haven't been forgotten.\n  \n   \nThis card's been a favorite of mine for a long time, and it's the epitome of blue's penchant for manipulation. I can't count the times I've used it, and how many outcomes it's yielded. Plus, it combos with so many things: Ritual of the Machine, Lord of Tresserhorn, Fling, Infernal Tribute, Carrion etc. Not to mention all the creatures that get buffs from sacrificing creatures.\n  \n   \nOh, Ray of Command, so many fond memories.",
      "posted_by": "RxPhantom",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost184729\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">First, I must say how pleased I am to see the <i>Mirage</i> art, and how happy I am that <i>Mirage</i> and <i>Visions</i> haven't been forgotten.\r<br/> <br/>This card's been a favorite of mine for a long time, and it's the epitome of blue's penchant for manipulation.  I can't count the times I've used it, and how many outcomes it's yielded.  Plus, it combos with so many things: Ritual of the Machine, Lord of Tresserhorn, Fling, Infernal Tribute, Carrion etc.  Not to mention all the creatures that get buffs from sacrificing creatures.\r<br/> <br/>Oh, Ray of Command, so many fond memories.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '184729'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy65073\">RxPhantom</span>\r\n                                (8/2/2011 10:18:47 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Im